With this patch tvmovie2vdr inserts the episode information into the EPG:

Eplist_Season: 04
Eplist_Episode: 22
Eplist_Number: 088

This can be used als search criterion in epgsearch etc.

Installation
------------

Go to the tvmovie2vdr source dir and do

patch -p1 < tvmovie2vdr-0.5.14-eplists-utf8-patch11.diff


Note: This patch changes all text in tvmovie2vdr into UTF-8.
